com.habelitz.jsobjectizer.jsom.api
Interface FormalParameterDeclaration

All Superinterfaces:
JSOM
public interface FormalParameterDeclaration
extends JSOM

This JSOM type represents a formal parameter declaration including vararg parameter declarations, i.e. a parameter declarations of a variable number of arguments like anyType ... typeId.

Author:
Dieter Habelitz
